{"tid":621677,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"「報定唔報」Oxford LLM","createTime":"2018-04-08T13:49:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-09T22:37:43.000Z","uid":180404,"like":19,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ac969f1b1c953d33f2333b951586892bd4670a40","tid":621677,"uid":180404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T13:49:01.000Z","msg":"前排send jor 我resume 去Oxford 到問我個 eligibility to a master programme (Part time)...之後收到reply (see below)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/08/212201_3e5d3dfcc6b30d8512a4a40b82c82288.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F08%2F212201_3e5d3dfcc6b30d8512a4a40b82c82288.png&h=ef9398e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n想問下各位巴絲點睇<br />\n<br />\n我profile:<br />\nSchool: GPA 3 (HK: second low; UK: second Up) <br />\nnon-law graduate, 非三大<br />\nExperience: 5 years relevant exp<br />\nQualification: HK, China, US &amp; UK<br />\n<br />\n諗住9月先報, 咩programme我就唔講啦, 同Law有關, 香港無e科, 要讀2年, 全英國都係得幾間有e科...就算唔報Oxford, 我都係報queen&rsquo;s, king&rsquo;s, LSE, Exeter..無咩options<br />\n<br />\n個programme唔係就gum報就得...仲要有3個referral, 同交一篇2萬字ge文<br />\n<br />\n老老77, 我讀書就真係唔算叻...入到e家e間公司個dept, 有一半原因都只係靠d大佬refer我先入到(唔請local grad). 相信當年個個巴絲張CV都靚過我<br />\n<br />\n其實最後我都係睇有無時間寫個篇文,不過都想聽下意見..有無人試過? 報唔報好? 通常外國d LLM有幾難？其實間學校係咪hea覆我?"},{"pid":"f06eb03805628fc6b95db655ad4ac149e7d29b17","tid":621677,"uid":180404,"like":17,"dislike":3,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T13:50:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 報<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔報"},{"pid":"9a5d1e5996aa92259a5f7889f9d0c8eff1ce0bcf","tid":621677,"uid":44593,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T13:51:50.000Z","msg":"寧願有嘗試過<br />\n最多都係失敗啫<br />\n報啦"},{"pid":"cb64c05716b5b8b5862b9a622fb71de15adb8511","tid":621677,"uid":123308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T13:52:45.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"18e687ba04ccdfe9d09753de4e01fe12bd9ab6c2","tid":621677,"uid":40839,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T13:55:18.000Z","msg":"機會微乎其微<br />\nOxford LLM(應該叫BCL) requirement係高到你讀Cambridge Law都要2nd+3rd year都拎1st class先夠<br />\n以前識人Cambridge Law 2nd year 2.i 3rd year 1st都唔收 最後留番原校讀LLM"},{"pid":"ed1884404a1abd462abb50aaed92cc9656bd93f0","tid":621677,"uid":40839,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"18e687ba04ccdfe9d09753de4e01fe12bd9ab6c2","tid":621677,"uid":40839,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T13:55:18.000Z","msg":"機會微乎其微<br />\nOxford LLM(應該叫BCL) requirement係高到你讀Cambridge Law都要2nd+3rd year都拎1st class先夠<br />\n以前識人Cambridge Law 2nd year 2.i 3rd year 1st都唔收 最後留番原校讀LLM"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T13:57:29.000Z","msg":"自膠 而家先睇到pt degree<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔熟 可試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1df6114c685463a94913de85a84f1735e44a75f9","tid":621677,"uid":166891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T14:01:03.000Z","msg":"加油啊 個grade可能差小小<br />\n最好你篇文寫到佢地覺得好有意思<br />\nimpress下佢地 <br />\n機會會大好多"},{"pid":"19366c690bd9a8f9e128a0e8b2b29be62ec03a73","tid":621677,"uid":180404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1df6114c685463a94913de85a84f1735e44a75f9","tid":621677,"uid":166891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T14:01:03.000Z","msg":"加油啊 個grade可能差小小<br />\n最好你篇文寫到佢地覺得好有意思<br />\nimpress下佢地 <br />\n機會會大好多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T14:04:51.000Z","msg":"個grade直頭係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n全個dept我最屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個個外國返, distinctions GPA 3.8, 3.9<br />\n<br />\n完全唔想留係個到...好似比人睇少gum"},{"pid":"3e